WEBVTT

00:00:44.362 --> 00:00:49.137
=The Hidden Heir Ye Chen=
(Adapted from "The Peerless Son-in-Law")

00:00:49.650 --> 00:00:52.250
=Episode 18=

00:00:58.560 --> 00:01:01.359
This flashy thing is all show
and no substance

00:01:01.359 --> 00:01:03.200
and you think it can save lives?

00:01:04.062 --> 00:01:05.850
If it doesn't end up
killing your daughter,

00:01:05.860 --> 00:01:07.439
you should already count yourself lucky.

00:01:07.719 --> 00:01:08.719
You're a major player

00:01:08.719 --> 00:01:10.519
in medicine business.

00:01:11.000 --> 00:01:12.519
What were you thinking?

00:01:14.640 --> 00:01:15.239
That's right.

00:01:15.760 --> 00:01:16.719
One careless moment,

00:01:16.719 --> 00:01:17.990
and we got fooled by a scoundrel.

00:01:18.599 --> 00:01:20.040
Dr. Shi, you must think poorly of us.

00:01:24.439 --> 00:01:25.079
Dad!

00:01:25.079 --> 00:01:25.680
Wait!

00:01:26.239 --> 00:01:27.190
What are you doing, Dad?

00:01:29.640 --> 00:01:31.239
Anything that can't save your sister

00:01:31.560 --> 00:01:32.359
is garbage.

00:01:32.560 --> 00:01:33.239
Throw it away.

00:01:33.760 --> 00:01:34.359
Garbage?

00:01:34.840 --> 00:01:36.079
This cost 100 million!

00:01:36.599 --> 00:01:37.680
You could've given it to me!

00:01:37.680 --> 00:01:38.770
Why would I give it to you?

00:01:38.787 --> 00:01:39.547
If I give you,

00:01:39.799 --> 00:01:41.200
you'd just get scammed too.

00:01:42.400 --> 00:01:44.200
Like you weren't scammed yourself!

00:01:48.159 --> 00:01:49.719
Anyway, how's Yu Jinghai?

00:01:50.519 --> 00:01:51.159
Erm...

00:01:51.400 --> 00:01:51.959
He's gone mad.

00:01:52.040 --> 00:01:52.760
Lost his mind.

00:01:52.812 --> 00:01:54.040
Can't get a word out of him.

00:01:54.640 --> 00:01:55.650
Don't worry.

00:01:56.159 --> 00:01:57.280
Now that I'm here,

00:01:58.400 --> 00:01:59.319
I'll do my best.

00:02:00.480 --> 00:02:01.159
Dr. Shi,

00:02:01.680 --> 00:02:02.840
thank you.

00:02:05.439 --> 00:02:06.959
Sorry. Mr. Qin isn't seeing guests.

00:02:08.719 --> 00:02:09.359
Mr. Qin.

00:02:09.500 --> 00:02:11.719
I just did you a huge favor,
and this is how you treat me?

00:02:11.720 --> 00:02:12.790
You do this on purpose, right?

00:02:18.660 --> 00:02:19.759
No, seriously, I surrender.

00:02:19.759 --> 00:02:21.300
Why are you here again?

00:02:22.639 --> 00:02:23.800
I need quiet.

00:02:24.199 --> 00:02:25.719
Stop making noise.

00:02:37.000 --> 00:02:38.790
White Tiger Head-Shaking
Acupuncture Technique?

00:02:41.120 --> 00:02:43.400
Young man, you know your stuff.

00:02:43.680 --> 00:02:44.919
To actually recognize

00:02:45.159 --> 00:02:46.280
my needle technique,

00:02:46.912 --> 00:02:47.840
you must come

00:02:48.199 --> 00:02:49.800
from a distinguished lineage.

00:02:51.080 --> 00:02:51.879
Sir,

00:02:51.879 --> 00:02:52.960
let me introduce him.

00:02:53.439 --> 00:02:55.000
He's no distinguished heir.

00:02:55.479 --> 00:02:56.639
He's the most famous

00:02:56.639 --> 00:02:58.510
good-for-nothing son-in-law
in all of Jinzhou.

00:02:58.759 --> 00:03:00.000
An orphaned loser.

00:03:01.000 --> 00:03:03.790
As a kid, I studied some acupuncture
with an old man for a couple of days.

00:03:03.800 --> 00:03:05.190
I've seen him demonstrate it before.

00:03:05.879 --> 00:03:07.759
But his needles
aren't nearly as nice as yours.

00:03:08.110 --> 00:03:09.319
They're just some metal spikes.

00:03:09.639 --> 00:03:12.400
To do a job well,
one must first sharpen his tools.

00:03:12.879 --> 00:03:15.159
Without my specially crafted
silver needles,

00:03:15.159 --> 00:03:16.000
it's impossible to perform

00:03:16.000 --> 00:03:18.319
the true White Tiger Head-Shaking
Acupuncture Technique

00:03:19.637 --> 00:03:22.378
I imagine that old man of yours

00:03:22.612 --> 00:03:25.087
must have picked up a few cheap tricks

00:03:25.462 --> 00:03:27.850
and went around swindling people
with them.

00:03:29.879 --> 00:03:30.520
Ye Chen,

00:03:30.700 --> 00:03:31.900
as you can see, I'm quite busy.

00:03:32.159 --> 00:03:33.800
Let's talk about our matter later.

00:03:34.039 --> 00:03:34.639
Guards!

00:03:35.120 --> 00:03:35.680
Wait.

00:03:36.412 --> 00:03:39.173
Since this young man
recognized the technique,

00:03:39.612 --> 00:03:41.240
I'll let him see

00:03:41.240 --> 00:03:44.100
what the real White Tiger Head-Shaking
Acupuncture Technique looks like.

00:03:44.390 --> 00:03:47.250
I've long heard that Dr. Shi
enjoys mentoring the younger generation.

00:03:47.575 --> 00:03:49.189
Truly the bearing of a great master.

00:03:49.450 --> 00:03:50.610
He just likes to show off.

00:03:52.487 --> 00:03:54.008
Close the windows and doors.

00:03:54.450 --> 00:03:56.368
Keep the evil winds out.

00:04:03.312 --> 00:04:04.673
At her three pulse points,

00:04:04.737 --> 00:04:06.696
the pulse is deep, rapid, and uneven.

00:04:09.925 --> 00:04:11.039
The toxin has sunk inward.

00:04:11.060 --> 00:04:12.420
She may only have seven days left.

00:04:14.240 --> 00:04:15.360
Her brow has darkened.

00:04:15.800 --> 00:04:16.759
The poison has gathered.

00:04:30.639 --> 00:04:32.240
Did her eyelid just move?

00:04:33.040 --> 00:04:33.480
Yes.

00:04:34.759 --> 00:04:35.600
What a miracle!

00:04:35.610 --> 00:04:38.160
The moment the needle stabbed her face,
her face flushed red right away!

00:04:38.160 --> 00:04:38.720
Right, Dad?

00:04:39.560 --> 00:04:39.839
Yes.

00:04:40.639 --> 00:04:41.639
Just a trivial trick.

00:04:42.160 --> 00:04:43.199
Not worth mentioning.

00:04:43.639 --> 00:04:44.480
Let me correct you.

00:04:44.680 --> 00:04:46.079
We don't call it stabbing.

00:04:46.199 --> 00:04:47.360
Instead, we physicians call it

00:04:47.560 --> 00:04:48.480
needle manipulation.

00:04:48.680 --> 00:04:49.800
Needle manipulation.

00:04:51.959 --> 00:04:52.839
So, young man,

00:04:53.959 --> 00:04:55.600
what do you think of my

00:04:55.620 --> 00:04:57.600
White Tiger Head-Shaking
Acupuncture Technique?

00:04:57.959 --> 00:05:00.519
How does it compare to
that old man you mentioned?

00:05:01.137 --> 00:05:02.200
As for the technique,

00:05:02.200 --> 00:05:03.800
you're certainly the older one.

00:05:04.399 --> 00:05:05.360
Watch your mouth!

00:05:05.360 --> 00:05:06.199
I mean seasoned,

00:05:06.839 --> 00:05:07.720
more experienced.

00:05:08.500 --> 00:05:09.720
But in terms of skill,

00:05:09.862 --> 00:05:11.050
it still lacks a bit.

00:05:11.337 --> 00:05:14.485
That old man once told me
that after performing this technique,

00:05:14.720 --> 00:05:17.387
even the gravest patient would wake up
for thirty to fifty minutes.

00:05:18.000 --> 00:05:20.500
But how come your patient seems
to have fallen asleep instead?

00:05:20.879 --> 00:05:22.079
Did you cut a corner?

00:05:22.120 --> 00:05:22.720
How...

00:05:23.867 --> 00:05:24.775
Insolence!

00:05:24.800 --> 00:05:26.397
I've cultivated my skills
for fifty years!

00:05:26.397 --> 00:05:27.077
Young man,

00:05:27.560 --> 00:05:29.480
what right does that old man have

00:05:29.480 --> 00:05:30.480
to judge my ability?

00:05:30.839 --> 00:05:32.480
Can't you see we're busy here?

00:05:32.480 --> 00:05:34.399
Stop bothering Dr. Shi, will you?

00:05:34.537 --> 00:05:35.737
You should leave now.

00:05:37.387 --> 00:05:38.775
Perhaps the doctor is tired.

00:05:39.262 --> 00:05:40.600
Shall I help you get some rest?

00:05:40.600 --> 00:05:41.839
I have fifty years of training.

00:05:41.839 --> 00:05:42.399
Me? Tired?

00:05:44.425 --> 00:05:45.560
Why are you so thick-skinned?

00:05:45.560 --> 00:05:46.450
Will you leave or not?

00:05:52.319 --> 00:05:53.319
If you're not tired,

00:05:53.319 --> 00:05:54.360
why not try again?

00:05:55.000 --> 00:05:56.000
I'll say this one last time,

00:05:56.000 --> 00:05:56.830
- if you...
- Wait.

00:05:57.399 --> 00:05:58.040
I...

00:05:59.962 --> 00:06:01.279
can try once more.

00:06:20.062 --> 00:06:21.447
She's awake!

00:06:22.879 --> 00:06:23.519
Aoxue.

00:06:25.437 --> 00:06:25.997
Dad...

00:06:27.090 --> 00:06:28.639
As long as you're awake, that's enough.

00:06:29.759 --> 00:06:30.519
Dr. Shi,

00:06:30.519 --> 00:06:32.160
your medical skills
are truly remarkable!

00:06:32.560 --> 00:06:33.759
Thank you.

00:06:33.759 --> 00:06:36.279
Your 50 years of mastery truly live up
to your name, Dr. Shi.

00:06:36.280 --> 00:06:37.990
If there's nothing else,
I'll take my leave.

00:06:38.879 --> 00:06:39.399
Wait.

00:06:40.439 --> 00:06:41.160
I'll see you out.

00:06:42.160 --> 00:06:43.240
No, you just woke up.

00:06:43.240 --> 00:06:43.800
Don't get up.

00:06:44.600 --> 00:06:46.120
Let her see the young man out.

00:06:46.560 --> 00:06:47.680
A little movement

00:06:47.775 --> 00:06:49.092
will do her good.

00:06:49.240 --> 00:06:49.879
Alright then.

00:06:50.240 --> 00:06:51.680
Careful now, slowly.

00:06:51.680 --> 00:06:52.879
Aoxue, take it slow.

00:06:54.870 --> 00:06:55.600
What's that smell?

00:06:55.600 --> 00:06:56.710
It actually smells pretty nice.

00:06:56.720 --> 00:06:57.079
There.

00:06:57.120 --> 00:06:57.879
It's that incense.

00:06:58.000 --> 00:07:00.279
My mom used to love burning this kind
when she was alive.

00:07:00.439 --> 00:07:01.319
I'm used to it.

00:07:01.319 --> 00:07:03.240
So whenever I spar,
I light a few sticks.

00:07:04.800 --> 00:07:06.500
Didn't you say you were going
to send me out.

00:07:06.519 --> 00:07:07.530
Why did you bring me here?

00:07:08.560 --> 00:07:10.959
About our last spar, I admitted defeat.

00:07:11.720 --> 00:07:13.439
But honestly,
I'm still a bit unconvinced.

00:07:13.680 --> 00:07:14.800
We should spar again.

00:07:14.800 --> 00:07:15.720
Alright.

00:07:16.399 --> 00:07:16.959
I give up.

00:07:17.279 --> 00:07:18.137
I give up, okay?

00:07:18.959 --> 00:07:19.399
Fine.

00:07:19.839 --> 00:07:20.879
If we're not sparring,

00:07:21.480 --> 00:07:23.759
could you teach me
those two moves you used to beat me?

00:07:24.120 --> 00:07:25.680
Once I learn them, we'll spar again.

00:07:26.120 --> 00:07:26.759
Forget it.

00:07:26.759 --> 00:07:28.500
The poison in your body
hasn't even been cured yet.

00:07:28.519 --> 00:07:30.737
It's fine. Isn't Dr. Shi here?

00:07:31.120 --> 00:07:32.000
Still, it's strange.

00:07:32.120 --> 00:07:33.587
My health has always been great.

00:07:33.625 --> 00:07:34.880
How could I have been poisoned?

00:07:36.959 --> 00:07:37.439
Aoxue,

00:07:38.100 --> 00:07:39.340
did it ever occur to you

00:07:39.487 --> 00:07:41.166
that when we sparred,

00:07:41.279 --> 00:07:42.759
I might've secretly poisoned you?

00:07:44.480 --> 00:07:45.600
What are you saying?

00:07:46.400 --> 00:07:48.879
Those two moves you used to beat me
were completely fair and square.

00:07:48.879 --> 00:07:51.350
You're not the kind of person
who'd poison someone behind their back.

00:07:51.360 --> 00:07:51.920
You're not.

00:07:53.600 --> 00:07:54.000
No.

00:07:54.000 --> 00:07:55.519
I still think we should spar again.

00:07:55.680 --> 00:07:56.399
Come on.

00:08:08.000 --> 00:08:08.560
Aoxue?

00:08:11.762 --> 00:08:12.614
Aoxue!

00:08:13.675 --> 00:08:14.560
Aoxue.

00:08:15.012 --> 00:08:15.731
Aoxue.

00:08:17.279 --> 00:08:18.000
Dr. Shi,

00:08:18.537 --> 00:08:18.977
this...

00:08:21.210 --> 00:08:23.120
What did you do
when you took her out just now?

00:08:23.360 --> 00:08:24.319
Why did she faint again?

00:08:24.319 --> 00:08:26.250
This matter is not the young man's fault.

00:08:28.480 --> 00:08:31.480
Mr. Qin, your daughter's poison
has already seeped deep into the marrow.

00:08:31.839 --> 00:08:32.780
The acupuncture just now

00:08:32.790 --> 00:08:34.800
was meant to draw the toxin outward
to the surface

00:08:34.800 --> 00:08:35.990
so it can be treated properly.

00:08:44.875 --> 00:08:46.593
The signs point to aconite toxicity.

00:08:48.480 --> 00:08:49.960
It's aconitine poisoning.

00:08:51.090 --> 00:08:51.799
It can be cured.

00:08:53.075 --> 00:08:54.660
Then we'll have to trouble you, Dr. Shi.

00:08:59.519 --> 00:09:01.915
With your fifty years of mastery,
we'll leave it to you.

00:09:03.400 --> 00:09:05.720
Ye Chen, I really don't have time
to entertain you today.

00:09:05.720 --> 00:09:06.650
Please see yourself out.

00:09:07.400 --> 00:09:08.200
Go on.

00:09:16.600 --> 00:09:17.639
Shi Tianqi?

00:09:17.862 --> 00:09:18.960
I've heard of him.

00:09:19.250 --> 00:09:20.892
He's a very famous miracle doctor.

00:09:21.200 --> 00:09:21.799
With him here,

00:09:22.000 --> 00:09:23.519
Qin Aoxue should be fine, right?

00:09:25.450 --> 00:09:27.440
That old man Shi
said it was aconitine poisoning,

00:09:28.000 --> 00:09:29.960
but something
about it still doesn't feel right.

00:09:33.559 --> 00:09:33.919
Oh yeah.

00:09:34.159 --> 00:09:34.559
Churan,

00:09:34.799 --> 00:09:35.879
accompany me tomorrow.

00:09:36.440 --> 00:09:36.960
Okay.

00:09:46.960 --> 00:09:48.639
(Goji berries.)

00:09:48.879 --> 00:09:50.039
(Hawthorn.)

00:09:50.720 --> 00:09:51.759
(Dried tangerine peel.)

00:09:52.159 --> 00:09:53.120
(Lily bulbs.)

00:09:53.639 --> 00:09:55.000
(Saffron.)

00:09:56.320 --> 00:09:58.799
(Grandpa, look! It's a bird's nest!)

00:09:59.825 --> 00:10:02.384
This is the place where you grew up?

00:10:02.775 --> 00:10:03.696
Yeah.

00:10:04.400 --> 00:10:06.090
How long has it been
since you came back?

00:10:07.519 --> 00:10:08.559
More than ten years.

00:10:11.840 --> 00:10:12.960
You didn't bring me here

00:10:13.200 --> 00:10:14.639
just for nostalgia, did you?

00:10:15.337 --> 00:10:16.840
Are you looking for something?

00:10:19.125 --> 00:10:20.758
Mr. Quan had a notebook.

00:10:20.987 --> 00:10:22.068
About this big.

00:10:22.300 --> 00:10:23.790
It contains records of many illnesses.

00:10:24.159 --> 00:10:25.360
Qin Aoxue's symptoms

00:10:25.840 --> 00:10:27.279
look very similar to one of them.

00:10:28.399 --> 00:10:29.000
Got it.

00:10:29.159 --> 00:10:30.039
I'll help you look.

00:10:30.480 --> 00:10:31.080
Let's go.

00:10:43.320 --> 00:10:43.919
Lil White,

00:10:44.487 --> 00:10:45.480
I'm back.

00:10:46.679 --> 00:10:47.720
Yintang Point.

00:10:49.840 --> 00:10:50.625
Tiantu Point.

00:10:53.240 --> 00:10:54.000
Long time no see.

00:10:55.919 --> 00:10:56.879
Who are you talking to?

00:10:58.519 --> 00:10:58.840
Come.

00:10:59.000 --> 00:10:59.750
Come here, Churan.

00:11:01.320 --> 00:11:03.519
Let me introduce you to my best friend
since childhood.

00:11:09.480 --> 00:11:10.475
It's okay.

00:11:10.879 --> 00:11:11.919
Don't be scared.

00:11:11.919 --> 00:11:12.919
- It's okay.
- You...

00:11:15.320 --> 00:11:16.039
Say hello.

00:11:16.039 --> 00:11:16.519
Shake hands.

00:11:16.960 --> 00:11:17.639
Come on.

00:11:18.112 --> 00:11:19.120
Hello.

00:11:19.120 --> 00:11:21.080
Miss Churan, you're very beautiful.

00:11:21.125 --> 00:11:22.084
Is this it?

00:11:22.162 --> 00:11:24.525
(Medical Log - Zuo Tradition
of the Spring and Autumn Annals)

00:11:28.000 --> 00:11:29.160
Good thing I brought you here.

00:11:34.200 --> 00:11:34.919
I knew it.

00:11:35.525 --> 00:11:37.525
Qin Aoxue wasn't poisoned
by aconitine at all.

00:11:56.125 --> 00:11:58.613
♪They said I was only meant
to gaze at the light♪

00:11:58.700 --> 00:12:02.453
♪Never knowing I am the flame itself♪

00:12:02.913 --> 00:12:07.850
♪I am fireworks, not a fire cast aside♪

00:12:08.013 --> 00:12:10.300
♪I open my eyes amid the ruins♪

00:12:10.613 --> 00:12:13.293
♪No one shields me
from the wind or the sky♪

00:12:14.363 --> 00:12:16.988
♪Let them mock, let them sneer♪

00:12:17.288 --> 00:12:20.300
♪I sharpen my silence into blades♪

00:12:20.500 --> 00:12:23.550
♪Every cold word, I remember♪

00:12:23.663 --> 00:12:26.625
♪Etching my path of defiance
into my heart♪

00:12:26.893 --> 00:12:30.050
♪Fate did not sign my future for me♪

00:12:30.275 --> 00:12:34.025
♪I carved my own light
with clenched fists♪

00:12:34.025 --> 00:12:36.888
♪I belong to no one♪

00:12:36.950 --> 00:12:40.400
♪I am the ember
that refuses to bow to destiny♪

00:12:40.400 --> 00:12:43.075
♪Even if the world burns me into ash♪

00:12:43.075 --> 00:12:49.413
♪I will rise upon those ashes♪